{"tid":1811063,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地要真雙普選, 唔係要唔公平既功能組別選舉, 我地要杯葛呢d唔公平選舉","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T17:19:40.000Z","uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0620079c90519eea148b363db3465c1c16bef78d","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"我地要真雙普選, 唔係要唔公平既功能組別選舉, 我地要杯葛呢d唔公平選舉<br />\n我知好多手足, 係咁諗, 而我都係咁諗<br />\n但現實係什麼, 大家要想清楚<br />\n<br />\n正如我地就算二百萬人, 全部要求正苦立即應承五大訴求, 正苦: 你痴撚左邊條線. 當然正苦唔會理你<br />\n我問呢d要求真雙普選既人, 你地話要杯葛功能組別呢d唔公平既選舉, 咁你地做乜可以令正苦比真雙普選我地? 但無人答到我<br />\n<br />\n有人答我, 美國支持我地取消功能組別, 支持香港有真雙普選. 美國其實到目前為止都係承認基本法同一國兩制, 美國支持我地取消功能組別, 都只係跟基本法行事<br />\n要取消功能組別就要修改基本法, 修改基本法其中一項就係要全體立法會議員2/3支持<br />\n你認為美國會為左香港, 然後派兵來支持香港? 所羅門都話美國會努力幫我地爭取能功組別商界既一票, 明白當中意思未?<br />\n<br />\n情況其實好似你落場踼波, 一開始判你輸左2球, 0:2<br />\n大把人話呢場球賽唔公平, 我地要杯葛呢場唔公平球賽<br />\n但現實係你得二個選擇<br />\n1. 0:2開始踼, 想贏要反超前3:2<br />\n2. 杯葛呢場唔公平球賽, 唔踼. 實際上等如輸左場波<br />\n杯葛=白票論<br />\n<br />\n如果你有更好選擇, 直接爭取公平選舉/球賽, 我點會唔同意呀<br />\n但現實係, 你去杯葛呢場唔公平既球賽, 唔踼. 等同你果隊踼小個, 仲要本身比數0:2"},{"pid":"b5d02c509e0ba0c3aa63c2dc49e62784d62c0959","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fb928b88af3552dcdbcec6fd74e37ae57968a7","tid":1811063,"uid":54014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"香港人無杯葛既本錢，理想中既唔踢係離開球場，現實中既唔踢係企定定係到，對面一樣照射你龍門。"},{"pid":"fb6bbe07437b6e43482474663c423f6fdf87efb8","tid":1811063,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:27:09.000Z","msg":"現實啲啦<br />\n你唔係住係英美澳加呢啲民主國家啊<br />\n喺中國啊"},{"pid":"ce41ed1cddd4bb9fe26663c516b0f1698e672895","tid":1811063,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41fb928b88af3552dcdbcec6fd74e37ae57968a7","tid":1811063,"uid":54014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"香港人無杯葛既本錢，理想中既唔踢係離開球場，現實中既唔踢係企定定係到，對面一樣照射你龍門。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n兩首詩--三問<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810144</a>"},{"pid":"ee10383e24c91d29c4265dd172fa0bbe39ed5ca0","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252c39329ba5a06769e9e6271a08b32a20124289","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0783f972286c24b35e5b100729f0d0372fbbda11","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c456128429fb4ace51dd2efb694457cec351edd2","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badeb947a92f998b482b031763f19ecfbad01585","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a70245b8c652942d69513dafd7072b2e305935","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2781268039a82a94d18b9e25a87e575a35e30045","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75443ef1f2cd8c1b349aef0f0fdce1395cb1f51d","tid":1811063,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"你係飯登講呢啲嘥撚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da49723c6ca06b6291f01fb8fc055edf867f3a57","tid":1811063,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔應該杯葛，所有方法都要去試<br />\n6月之前，大多數香港人係只去做最容易行果條路，靠晒代議士去&quot;議會抗爭&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但係自從6月，真正全民覺醒，香港人明白唔單止靠代議士去抗爭，議員有議員角色，和理非有和理非角色，勇武有勇武角色<br />\n<br />\n依家諗清楚，當初我地係反對議會抗爭，抑或係反對<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只進行</span></strong>議會抗爭<br />\n<br />\n只要唔係行番回頭路，淨係投完票選議員就當做左野，就冇理由反對<br />\n冇大台，各自爬山，就係乜都試，有機會贏到既就要去做"},{"pid":"9cb4ffaacf32b681244fc3cc11416212cb409b58","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcc2b48854551943b811b9dc6f4447d1e095ae4","tid":1811063,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:25:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說「新沙士」 <br />\n試著說「中國肺炎」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"60c668a2d4a250550a78ac6c6463d6e457ac4d6b","tid":1811063,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"如果剷平呢個制度呢?"},{"pid":"dffea3650621822a72074714506e114800da4ba3","tid":1811063,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec48895c4615cd765df46295a57f01ad34493d4","tid":1811063,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"我地係要推翻呢個政府<br />\n唔係要同佢玩選舉"},{"pid":"32669b2cf2ef8a73547dbaee2776e46cd2a3d4bb","tid":1811063,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ec48895c4615cd765df46295a57f01ad34493d4","tid":1811063,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"我地係要推翻呢個政府<br />\n唔係要同佢玩選舉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"支持你效仿黃興先賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}